Outline of a compiler

1) Lexical Analysis  -- Syntactic
2) Parsing           -- Syntactic
3) Semantic Analysis -- Types, Scopes 
4) Optimization
5) Code Generation   -- Translation

Modern Compiler: 
------------------------------------
| L | P |   S   |      O      | CG |  
------------------------------------
Small Lexical Analyzer, Parser and Code Generator,
Moderate Syntactic analyzer, very large Optimizer

